5 other companions (including a Gondor companion) <br />
Seeing Stone of Orthanc <br />
<br />
Hand with 4 Khazad Ai-Menu and 4 Tidings of Erebor <br />
<br />
Start of Turn <br />
------------- <br />
Draw a random FP card with Gandalf <br />
<br />
Fellowship Phase <br />
---------------- <br />
Use EMHR to take 4 Flurry of Blows into hand <br />
<br />
Skirmish Phases <br />
--------------- <br />
Win a skirmish with Gandalf and exert him 4 times <br />
to draw 8 random FP cards <br />
Win a fierce skirmish with Gandalf and exert him twice <br />
to draw 4 Battle Fury <br />
Use Sindri and exert Sindri <br />
to play Out of Darkness from HiGR <br />
to draw 2 random FP cards <br />
<br />
<br />
Regroup Phase <br />
------------- <br />
Use Steadfast Champion to heal Gandalf 3 times <br />
Play 4 Tidings of Erebor to draw 12 random FP cards <br />
Add 9 threats and discard Seeing Stone to draw 10 random FP cards <br />
Double move past Minas Tirith Fifth Circle to heal Gandalf 3 times <br />
<br />
<br />
Double Move Skirmish Phases <br />
--------------------------- <br />
Win 2 more skirmishes with Gandalf and exert him 6 times <br />
to draw 12 random FP cards <br />
Start Gimli&#39;s skirmish. He is currently damage (+8) <br />
Stack 4 Flurry of Blows on HiGR (+12) <br />
Stack 4 Khazad Ai-Menu on HiGR (+16) <br />
Stack 4 Battle Fury on HiGR (+20) <br />
Use Sindri to play 4 Flurry of Blows (+24) <br />
Use Sindri to play 4 Khazad Ai-Menu (+28) <br />
Use Sindri and exert Gimli 4 times (+32) <br />
to play 4 Battle Fury (+36) <br />
Use Sindri and exert Gimli 3 times (+39) <br />
to play 3 Out of Darkness from HiGR <br />
to draw 6 random FP cards <br />
Stack 51 FP cards from hand on HiGR (+90) <br />
Play Honed with Sindri from EMHR for +90 <br />
